  "comment": "Light Sources:\n1x 200W 4IN1 RGBW LED\n24x 0.1 W 3IN1 RGB LED\nWorking hour: ≥20000h\nBeam Angle: 4.4°~52.4°\nPower Consumption: 196W±5%W\nPower Voltage: AC 100-240V, 50/60Hz\nDimension: 303*230*409mm\nNet Weight: 9 Kgs\nFlight case packing 6in1 size: 950*630*585mm\nGross weight：83.5Kg\nCarton package 1in1 size: 460*325*385mm\nGross weight: 11.8 Kg\n\nMaximum number of connections: \n16 units (230V, 50Hz) 2.5mm² power cable\n8 units (120V, 60Hz) 2.5mm² power cable\n\nControl:\nDMX Channel: 20 /30/13CH\nControl Modes: DMX512/Master-Slave/Auto Run/Music/RDM/Artnet\n\nPan/Tilt:\nPan/Tilt: 540°/ 270°\nPan/Tilt Resolution: 8/16 bit\n\nConstruction:\nDisplay: TFT 1.8 inch Display\nData In/Out socket: 3-pin XLR sockets\nPower Socket: Power con in/out\nProtection Rating: IP20\n\nFeatures:\nFull light range dimmng,256-level dimming adcuracy; fast strobe 1~25Hz;\nPixel control of lamp beads; preset multiple color macro functions;\n200W lamp beads can be imaged and rotated/atomized;preset multiple effect (pixel control, strobe) macro functions",
